CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 2, 1952, pg. 19, reads: "Strong Men - Three of the men who attend the weekly weight lifting classes now being conducted at the Kay Boys Club are pictured above. From left to right: Ernest Pollard, Edward Pollard, and William Brown.  The classes are open to the public.  Courses in ju-jitsu are also being conducted."
TitMainTitle: Three male weight lifters, Ernest Pollard, Edward Pollard, and William Brown, posing in the Kay Boys Club
